    <item>
      <title>南非将外交政策与经济利益相结合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/south-africa-to-align-foreign-policy-with-economic-interests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非新成立的商业友好型联合政府表示，其外交政策将侧重于促进国家的经济利益，这一转变可能有助于修复与其最大贸易伙伴西方国家之间的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/south-africa-to-align-foreign-policy-with-economic-interests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 08:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
